{"tid":812524,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"西班牙菜食評 - Rustico","createTime":"2018-09-09T16:42:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-07T02:17:30.000Z","uid":175988,"like":3,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"cee6e6dd3496f679dd2e8312459aadcd095fd091","tid":812524,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-09T16:42:48.000Z","msg":"<strong>Rustico @ 荔枝角</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/tcLZJbM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtcLZJbM.jpg&h=3c10f3e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>西班牙海鮮飯</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n海鮮份量算多，意外地有海水䶢香，蜆唔大隻但多汁，大蝦肉質爽彈唔霉<br />\n<br />\n飯底偏乾但滲有海產嘅鮮味，特別在混有魷魚同臘肉粒，口感提升咗唔少<br />\n<br />\n鐵鑊可以保持食物温度，擺得耐咗都唔會凍哂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n米粒唔夠煙韌，質感過硬，有啲未煮透嘅感覺<br />\n<br />\n薄薄一層飯底，同海鮮份量上比例失衡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: 香港嚟講算高質，值得一試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong>"},{"pid":"2f65e5fcee9be869a9809a2ef585baaff0ed9b69","tid":812524,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T02:09:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01146cec60f80edc39a2cb3d314bc03d539ce523","tid":812524,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T04:11:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07087552a7964102f25d606214c51375e743aa31","tid":812524,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"幾$先"},{"pid":"59f4e820a5d115fa32cda55303223b1210328526","tid":812524,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"07087552a7964102f25d606214c51375e743aa31","tid":812524,"uid":16697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T04:42:24.000Z","msg":"